heading: Wretched Delve Dungeon Guide
content: Wretched Delve is contains a valuable damage aspect for early game Lighting Sorcerers, the . a quick and easy completion time, and simple objectives. Stock up on your Sigils for this one; you'll run it over and over again for massive hordes of loot! While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! This dungeon is not accessible until you cleanse out the evil in . This unlocks the Dungeon along with potential vendors and a waypoint. This can be done solo, but goes by quicker with a group of friends. Reviewed by
